---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="FAQ - Circular Horizons International">
  <div class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl">
          Frequently Asked Questions
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-600">
          Find answers to common questions about our services and solutions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <summary class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">What is a circular economy?</summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">A circular economy is an economic system aimed at eliminating waste and the continual use of resources. It contrasts with a traditional linear economy, which has a 'take, make, dispose' model.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <summary class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">How can Circular Horizons help my business?</summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">We provide consultancy services, technology platforms, and expert guidance to help your business transition to sustainable practices, reduce environmental impact, and achieve your ESG goals.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <summary class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">What industries do you work with?</summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">We work with organizations across all sectors, including manufacturing, retail, hospitality, finance, and more. Our solutions are tailored to meet the specific needs of each industry.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <summary class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">What is ESG reporting?</summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">ESG stands for Environmental, Social, and Governance. ESG reporting involves measuring and disclosing your company's performance across these three pillars to stakeholders and investors.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <summary class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 cursor-pointer">How do I get started?</summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Simply contact us through our contact page, and one of our experts will reach out to discuss your needs and how we can help you achieve your sustainability goals.</p>
        </details>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Still have questions?</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90">
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
